                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820911-64-off335 t17820911-64-cd336"></join> last, on e silver watch, value 40 s. one silver chain, value 20 s. and one silver seal, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17820911-64-victim743" type="victimName">
